DISCLAIMER FOR HEALTHCARE USE:

This software is provided for use in healthcare data transformation and
migration workflows. Users of this software in a healthcare context are
responsible for ensuring compliance with all applicable laws and regulations,
including but not limited to:

- Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA)
- State and local healthcare privacy laws
- Data protection regulations (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)
- Institutional policies and procedures

This software does NOT automatically ensure HIPAA or other regulatory compliance.
Organizations using this software for healthcare data must:

1. Conduct their own compliance assessments
2. Obtain appropriate Business Associate Agreements (BAAs)
3. Implement necessary technical and organizational security measures
4. Consult with legal counsel regarding regulatory requirements
5. Maintain comprehensive audit logs and documentation
6. Train staff on proper data handling procedures

See the compliance.md file for additional guidance on healthcare compliance.
